{"tid":94602,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"港航大派2.5-3個月花紅 3000員工受惠","createTime":"2017-01-25T10:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T01:35:41.000Z","uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19528da46fb5c3c9b4fad6e104be2e1fa04a8a0e","tid":94602,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:31:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://topick.hket.com/article/1636409/%E6%B8%AF%E8%88%AA%E5%A4%A7%E6%B4%BE%E8%8A%B1%E7%B4%852.5%E8%87%B33%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E3%80%803%E5%8D%83%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%8F%97%E6%83%A0?r=cpsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1636409%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2588%25AA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%25B4%25852.5%25E8%2587%25B33%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E3%2580%25803%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%2583%25A0%3Fr%3Dcpsdfb&d=stq8Yq4x3zB%2BCqDDIAkaGnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=d9942312\" target=\"_blank\">http://topick.hket.com/article/1636409/%E6%B8%AF%E8%88%AA%E5%A4%A7%E6%B4%BE%E8%8A%B1%E7%B4%852.5%E8%87%B33%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E3%80%803%E5%8D%83%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%8F%97%E6%83%A0?r=cpsdfb</a><br />\n<br />\n香港航空傳喜訊！香港航空發言人證實，港航本月已向員工派發2個月花紅，今天再出通知，因2016 年業績表現理想，董事會通過，2月會再派多0.5至1個月糧作特別花紅，受惠員工包括空中服務人員、機師、地勤及後勤人員約3,000人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港航去年新增了11條新航綫，而客運量按年增加約80萬，達660萬人次。發言人指出，今年港航將會繼續新增航線，包括今年6月30日起，正式開通每日一班往來香港至溫哥華國際機場的直航服務，而部分現有航線亦會加密。"},{"pid":"1d4bc9c45d027169d75e011da813f85cf5a7ace4","tid":94602,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:33:32.000Z","msg":"望番格離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46009f28359b987914c48c27639dc485e89e1924","tid":94602,"uid":9708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:35:06.000Z","msg":"因航雞又要跪地罷工了"},{"pid":"14aab9410eccf6984b7a82da3ef09b4d986d3a85","tid":94602,"uid":3482,"like":0,"disl